items.summary: Move the four selected elements so they appear together as the last content within their current parent container, preserving their internal order and without changing any other parts of the page. The elements to move are exactly those located at these XPaths: (1) `/html[1]/body[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[5]/div[1]`, (2) `/html[1]/body[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[5]/div[1]/div[2]/div[1]/div[1]`, (3) `/html[1]/body[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[5]/div[1]/div[2]/div[3]/div[1]`, (4) `/html[1]/body[1]/div[1]/div[2]/div[5]/div[1]/div[2]/div[4]/p[1]`.
